{"tid":402552,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]石元泰博重回連登兼送上經典寫真","createTime":"2017-09-16T13:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T15:01:08.000Z","uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"698b0aa3fa36d0efc7b2dc84b4e01f357850d7a5","tid":402552,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"大家好，石元泰博終於返返黎啦<br />\n過去兩個月，我經歷左人生高山低谷<br />\n終於我覺得以往實在錯得太緊要<br />\n決定覺今是而昨非，跪地認過<br />\n過去恩怨情仇一筆勾銷<br />\n並且用全新形象見大家<br />\n保證真石元，勁泰博<br />\n<br />\n附上經典寫真《桂離宮》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/214817_912552c414fdef6145586085200f564a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F214817_912552c414fdef6145586085200f564a.jpg&h=f271c331&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23c758be1697ec6953b8e332eddf59e3f8b7b5ac","tid":402552,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f27feb3652dca55ee686bba30ce3cf6f031a1ed","tid":402552,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔貼自拍上位嗱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要上位果個唔係我播😏😏😏<br />\n邊個係都要谷起隻抽post有眼見。<br />\n<br />\n而且我潛心向佛<br />\n都係修心養性好啲"},{"pid":"cfe0457e6261b9886d6d16d382f25801caa5aca0","tid":402552,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b637bec8fa9d145ec122277fe1c4c83fb722ac46","tid":402552,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔貼自拍上位嗱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要上位果個唔係我播😏😏😏<br />\n邊個係都要谷起隻抽post有眼見。<br />\n<br />\n而且我潛心向佛<br />\n都係修心養性好啲</blockquote><br />\n噉關你無啦啦自貼咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行得正企得正<br />\n自貼最多只係戇鳩姐<br />\n<br />\n總好過有人一直收埋自己搞小動作扮智者😏😏😏"},{"pid":"529780d8443e8ed6304497bb40486d40561873af","tid":402552,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e77f147a0b89940bd54cea35248ce8f5929ed2b","tid":402552,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次返黎，我練成左獨門秘技：<br />\n<br />\n石原讀心術<br />\n<br />\n你個表情既意思係：<br />\n<br />\n姣婆守唔到寡"},{"pid":"ac11de2b7967dcb727d50f4b3353558d9f00abaf","tid":402552,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:41:52.000Z","msg":"開真身見人"},{"pid":"953b44382766a33cd6b97f91394369d253833f70","tid":402552,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開真身見人</blockquote><br />\n😏😏😏我應該一直用緊真身擋既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/230106_0628620ad98d8dd822cee84de3cbc3a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F230106_0628620ad98d8dd822cee84de3cbc3a4.jpg&h=edcdaa76&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}